@430 = ~Claws~ 

@440 = ~SORCERER: Scions of innately magical bloodlines, the chosen of deities, the spawn of monsters, pawns of fate and destiny, or simply flukes of fickle magic, sorcerers look within themselves for arcane prowess and draw forth might few mortals can imagine. Emboldened by lives ever threatening to be consumed by their innate powers, these magic-touched souls endlessly indulge in and refine their mysterious abilities, gradually learning how to harness their birthright and coax forth ever greater arcane feats.

FEATURES
- May become proficient (+) in Clubs, Daggers, Staffs, Crossbows, Darts, and Slings. 
- May not wear armor. 
- May cast arcane spells. 
- May declare a Sorcerous Bloodline.  
- Has a permanent -1 casting speed penalty, which determines several class features and Bloodline bonus spells.
- Hit Die: d4 
~ 

