@1141 = ~BATTLEMAGE: Battlemages are followers of the traditions of the War Wizards of Cormyr, an elite and highly respected group of Mages and Sorcerers, all loyal servants of the Crown of Cormyr. Through extensive training in both combat and arcane magic, War Wizards become able to blend the two together, typically with great effect. 

