@1142 = ~shadow adept~
@1143 = ~Shadow Adept~
@1144 = ~SHADOW ADEPT: A few mages reject the Weave as the source of their magical energy and instead begin to use the Shadow Weave to fuel their arcane powers. Users of the Shadow Weave gain great power over certain schools of magic, but find themselves unable to draw on the Weave, barring them from certain other schools entirely. 

